---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Shiba Inu Quizzes - Test Your Knowledge | Life with Yukki"
  description="Fun and informative quizzes about Shiba Inu dogs. Find out if a Shiba Inu is right for you, test your breed knowledge, and more."
  alternateUrls={{ en: '/quizzes/', ru: '/ru/testy/' }}
>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Shiba Inu Quizzes</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">Interactive quizzes to help you learn about this amazing breed</p>
      </div>

      <div class="quizzes-grid">
        <a href="/quizzes/is-shiba-right-for-you" class="quiz-card card">
          <div class="quiz-icon">üêï</div>
          <h2>Is a Shiba Inu Right for You?</h2>
          <p>Answer 10 questions to find out if a Shiba Inu matches your lifestyle, living situation, and personality.</p>
          <span class="quiz-meta">
            <span class="quiz-time">5 min</span>
            <span class="quiz-questions">10 questions</span>
          </span>
          <span class="btn">Take Quiz</span>
        </a>

        <div class="quiz-card card coming-soon">
          <div class="quiz-icon">üé®</div>
          <h2>What Shiba Color Matches You?</h2>
          <p>Discover which Shiba Inu coat color reflects your personality - Red, Sesame, Black & Tan, or Cream.</p>
          <span class="quiz-meta">
            <span class="quiz-time">3 min</span>
            <span class="quiz-questions">8 questions</span>
          </span>
          <span class="btn btn-disabled">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>

        <div class="quiz-card card coming-soon">
          <div class="quiz-icon">üß†</div>
          <h2>Shiba Inu Breed Knowledge Test</h2>
          <p>Think you know everything about Shiba Inus? Test your knowledge about their history, traits, and care.</p>
          <span class="quiz-meta">
            <span class="quiz-time">5 min</span>
            <span class="quiz-questions">15 questions</span>
          </span>
          <span class="btn btn-disabled">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .page-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      color: var(--color-primary);
      font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .page-subtitle {
      font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
      color: var(--color-text-light);
    }

    .quizzes-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-xl);
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .quiz-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    a.quiz-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    }

    .quiz-card.coming-soon {
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .quiz-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .quiz-card h2 {
      color: var(--color-primary);
      font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .quiz-card p {
      color: var(--color-text-light);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
      flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .quiz-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      color: var(--color-text-light);
    }

    .quiz-time::before {
      content: '‚è±Ô∏è ';
    }

    .quiz-questions::before {
      content: 'üìù ';
    }

    .btn-disabled {
      background-color: var(--color-text-light);
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .btn-disabled:hover {
      background-color: var(--color-text-light);
      transform: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .quizzes-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
